The wait is over — Thunderbolts has hit theaters, and the Major Issues Podcast is here to break down Marvel Studios’ latest blockbuster! Packed with fan-favorite antiheroes, high-stakes action, and shocking twists, this isn’t your typical Avengers lineup — or is it? Join us as we dive into the movie’s biggest moments, standout performances (Bucky! Yelena! Red Guardian!), and what this misfit team means for the future of the MCU. From secret missions to unexpected alliances, Thunderbolts brings the heat — and we’ve got thoughts. Marvel’s wildest ride yet? Let’s talk about it!

Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by ComicBook Clique, the only stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

